<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>CSE Motors</title>
<style>
  /* Background Checkerboard Pattern */
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: #000;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(45deg, #fff 25%, transparent 25%),
      linear-gradient(-45deg, #fff 25%, transparent 25%),
      linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 75%, #fff 75%),
      linear-gradient(-45deg, transparent 75%, #fff 75%);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
    background-position: 0 0, 0 20px, 20px -20px, -20px 0px;
  }
  /* Container */
  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 40px auto;
    background: #fff;
    border: 6px solid #0a9bd4;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 20px 30px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    color: #000;
  }
  /* Header Styles */
  header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  header h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 2em;
  }
  header .account-link {
    font-size: 0.9em;
    color: #333;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  /* Navigation Bar */
  nav {
    background-color: #1a1a2e;
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 10px 0;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  nav a {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }
  nav a:hover,
  nav a:focus {
    background-color: #0a9bd4;
    outline: none;
  }

  /* Welcome Section */
  .welcome-section {
    display: flex;
    gap: 30px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .welcome-text {
    max-width: 250px;
  }
  .welcome-text h2 {
    color: #0a9bd4;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .welcome-text ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    padding: 0;
    color: #008cc4;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .welcome-text ul li {
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .btn-own {
    background-color: #0a9bd4;
    border: none;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    font-weight: bold;
    border-radius: 5px;
    cursor: pointer;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(10,155,212,0.4);
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }
  .btn-own:hover,
  .btn-own:focus {
    background-color: #0585c0;
    outline: none;
  }
  img.car-image {
    max-width: 350px;
    height: auto;
    border: 2px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  /* Main Content Flex Layout */
  .main-content {
    display: flex;
    gap: 40px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  /* Upgrades Section */
  .upgrades {
    flex: 1 1 300px;
  }
  .upgrades h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .upgrades-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .upgrade-item {
    text-align: center;
  }
  .upgrade-item img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 150px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  .upgrade-item img:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }
  .upgrade-item a {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 8px;
    color: #0a9bd4;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .upgrade-item a:hover,
  .upgrade-item a:focus {
    text-decoration: underline;
    outline: none;
  }

  /* Reviews Section */
  .reviews {
    flex: 1 1 300px;
  }
  .reviews h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .reviews ul {
    padding-left: 20px;
  }
  .reviews ul li {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* Footer */
  footer {
    margin-top: 30px;
    font-size: 0.85em;
    color: #666;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Responsive Adjustments */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .main-content {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .welcome-section {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    img.car-image {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }
  }

</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>CSE Motors</h1>
      <div class="account-link" tabindex="0">My Account</div>
    </header>

    <nav>
      <a href="#">Home</a>
      <a href="#">Custom</a>
      <a href="#">Sedan</a>
      <a href="#">SUV</a>
      <a href="#">Truck</a>
    </nav>

    <section class="welcome-section" aria-label="Welcome section">
      <div class="welcome-text">
        <h2 tabindex="0">DMC Delorean</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>3 Cup holders</li>
          <li>Superman doors</li>
          <li>Fuzzy dice!</li>
        </ul>
        <button class="btn-own" aria-label="Own DMC Delorean today">Own Today</button>
      </div>
      <img src="public/images/vehicles/delorean.jpg" alt="DMC Delorean car" class="car-image" />
    </section>

    <div class="main-content">
      <section class="upgrades" aria-labelledby="upgrades-title">
        <h3 id="upgrades-title">Delorean Upgrades</h3>
        <div class="upgrades-grid">
          <div class="upgrade-item">
            <img src="public/images/upgrades/flux-cap.png" alt="Flux Capacitor upgrade" />
            <a href="#">Flux Capacitor</a>
          </div>
          <div class="upgrade-item">
            <img src="public/images/upgrades/flame.jpg" alt="Flame Decals upgrade" />
            <a href="#">Flame Decals</a>
          </div>
          <div class="upgrade-item">
            <img src="public/images/upgrades/bumper_sticker.jpg" alt="Bumper Stickers upgrade" />
            <a href="#">Bumper Stickers</a>
          </div>
          <div class="upgrade-item">
            <img src="public/images/upgrades/hub-cap.jpg" alt="Hub Caps upgrade" />
            <a href="#">Hub Caps</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="reviews" aria-labelledby="reviews-title">
        <h3 id="reviews-title">DMC Delorean Reviews</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>"So fast it's almost like traveling in time." (4/5)</li>
          <li>"Coolest ride on the road." (4/5)</li>
          <li>"I'm feeling McFly!" (5/5)</li>
          <li>"The most futuristic ride of our day." (4.5/5)</li>
          <li>"80's livin and I love it!" (5/5)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>

    <footer>
      &copy; 2023, CSE 340 App
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
